markets.title: Will Caedrel have more than 300k concurrent viewers in 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If Caedrel has more than 300k concurrent viewers on Twitch, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
A clarification for this market has been posted below 08/21/2025:

The title has been updated to: “Will Caedrel have more than 300k concurrent viewers during Worlds?” This change was made to align with the rulebook variable, which specifies “during Worlds” as the relevant time period.
